content.detailedDescription: Early one evening around 830 or 9 pm back in 2015 around the middle of june i was home and stepped out to my front porch to have a cigar as usual. i had just sat down on the porch swing and turned to face north,when i saw 2 or three round orb objects glowing with an undulating fire which appeared to be coming from its interior but the objects also appeared to have a definitive edge outlining their perfect orb shape.They came from the east and traveled west.They were not an equal distance from each other and moved with a swooping changing of direction ,almost a spiraling or balloon type of movement ,and mostly appeared as balloons tied together. but with a horizontal speed of about 80-100 mph. the way they appeared tied together as they traveled west is the way that they changed altitude by 50-100 feet or so and also in a snake like fashion side to side by just as much. they looked to be the size of large cars or trucks, that were 500 ft up and 1/4 mile out, definitely a strange flight path. so i smoked and went inside . and could not stop thinking about the three weird fire balloons tied together flying by like a snake.Thats when things got interesting when i went back outside on the porch to gaze into the sky and ponder what i just saw. then all of a sudden here come three more over the tree top from the very same direction ,so i ran out to the street to follow a line of sight on them as they also moved west. then one more came over the tree top then two more then about four more appeared over the trees to the east of me . a total of about 8 or ten they all appeared to be tied together by some invisible thread as they snaked their way to the west.Even though they were all at different distances to each other.Just  as the last of  them went by i heard my neighbors holler out ,hey look at that !! and i hollered back at them ...Did you see that ? they all replied yes! i never went to their house and questioned them about that night ,but i also cant stop thinking about it either . that brings me here. thanks for listening william
content.summary: I went out for a cigarette and saw them coming right past my line of sight as i looked up

content.detailedDescription: I was 6 or 7 years old. i was a wake by sounds coming from my back yard.  i went to look out the bath room window. at first i saw the craft. it was already landed. then i saw two greys aliens coming tored my house, no more than 20 ft. i was scare and ran back to my beds, my brother wasn't home, we share a bunk beds. i got on the bottom bunk and covered my self up. a few years later i felt a bump on my west. it was black. i was around 11 years old. i started to pick at it. it look  like a piece of lead from a pencil, the object was write under my skin. i got a needle and tweezer started picking at it. after 30 minute i notice it was black rounded at the front with two small hooks on the back. it was the hooks holding it in attach to my attendant or muscle. findly one side pop up and i was able to squeeze the area and the object pop out into the grass. i hardly ever talk about it. don't remember the time lost or the abduction. my second time seeing a ufo was in charleston south carolina. i was 19/20 driving north on hwy 78 i was in my new corvette. i was driving around 60 mile a hour. a white ball of light started to follow me, the whole object was glowing. it follow me for 5 miles and for some reason i decided to stop a check it out. again i dont remember the abduction. butt when i got to my friend house i was about a hour late. true i am 58 you never forget.

content.detailedDescription:
This happened to me around 10 years ago. i went to the indianapolis airport to pick up my mother who was flying in from sarasota fl. i cant even tell you what time of year it was or an exact date. however this happened just after sunset and early twilight was the time. this could be found in records from flights and visits my mother has made back home here just not sure. we were driving south on i 65 around mm 95 just past the whiteland exit. i looked out my drivers side window and up and seen this huge thing mabey 500 to 1000 feet going south. it was going slightly faster than we were as it was passing us. i shouted to my mom "what the hell is that"? i was driving and she told me to pay attention to the road and she would look. my first thought is that it was a blimp. however this was much larger like at least 3 or 4 times and not shaped like a blimp but a wedge or triangle. i also know blimps cant go that fast as we were going 75 or so and was passing us. i only got a few glimpses and to this day don't know why i didn't pull over and look. as i remember there was lights and detail like symbols on it. the angles were sharp on the craft and it was in a way box shaped meaning the triangle had right angles and flat surface. too this day i don't know what we had seen. my mother is 74 years old and lives in venice fl and was with me and a witness the whole time. we both told a few friends about it as we were both confused at what we had seen and really amazed nothing was reported. we got a lot a jokes like what were you drinking or smoking exct. so we kinda just left it there. we have talked about it a few times but the jokes from the very few we told made us feel like we should just shut up. i know the date and info is somewhat sketchy, however my mother and i know we seen something. what it was i have no idea but too this day i wonder.
thanks
content.summary: It was a very large triangle shaped craft with vertical sides and lights. well over 3 football fields it was traveling slightly faster than i was on i 65 at 70mph

content.detailedDescription: I sometimes like to look for satellites i was at my moms she lived in the country about 8 miles west of collinsville. it's about 10 pm and iam lying on the hood of my car i saw 2 satellites past over moving from north to south around 12 minutes apart. then in less than a minute i saw a third satellite moving from north to south for about 20 seconds from when i first spotted it. then suddenly changed direction to the west at a speed so fast that in less than a second it was gone. i don't remember my moms address she passed away many years ago. l felt amazed  at what i saw. i told a few people about what i had seen. but no one cared. so why tell about this now because i just wanted to tell someone who maybe cares.
content.summary: I was watching  satelites moving from north to south. while watching this satellite move from north to south after about  15 to 20 seconds it changed direction west  at very  high speed. it disappeared in less than a second.

content.detailedDescription:
On a clear october evening in 1977, my brother, boyfriend and a friend that lived at the mentioned address were returning from (i don't remember where we had been, but most likely we went to the store or a friends place). 
my brother was driving and we pulled into the driveway and began to exit the car. as we began to step out of the car something made us look up i continued to exit the car the whole time looking up at this craft. it was dark in color, and had no lights. 
when telling others about it soon after the incident i described it as a trojan bird. many years later when i saw the stealth bomber, it looked very similar to what i saw. the major difference was the incredibly slow speed it was traveling. it took 5 to 10 seconds to travel about 75 feet only 10 to 100 feet above us. we lost sight of it as it passed over the house behind us. i was stunned, not afraid, but i knew it as a physical impossibility to be so massive yet fly so slowly. 

thank you for allowing me to share my story, after so many years.
content.summary: A black stealth like looking object, that made no noise although it was extremely close to us

the object was static on that position: not moved from the first sight to until i leave. it remains the same no clouds getting into those void spaces with a triangular shape. my feeling was normal,i just want to go home and rest and maybe share the picture with my coworker some day.

content.detailedDescription: Sitting in backyard around dusk this object with a bright light came toward us, once we saw it we stood up perplexed as to what it was. it seemed to be about 500 feet or so in the air. i believe it noticed us and as soon as we stood up an took notice the bright light went off. the object made no sound and had pulsating lights on the bottom in a circular fashion. it made absolutely no sound at all, it was not a balloon or plane or anything like the such. it flew in a fairly direct line heading north over our heads and the farm we were at. we moved toward it as it was moving and it flew right over our heads , we walked heading north and followed it. it headed out over the highway and then we lost site of it. it looked as though it was heading out over the lake towards michigan. there were three of us there and each one of us saw it. i would have never believed in ufo's until i saw this thing.
content.summary: Saucer or bell shaped with lights on bottom rotating in a circular motion - had bright light facing ground until it seen us.

content.detailedDescription: A person i worked with and myself were standing on the porch of the second story of our barracks. at holloman afb, nm. about midnight when we saw a light moving across the clear sky. we could observe very due to the lack of moon light.  the light moved about the speed of a small aircraft from west to east until it reached about 1/4 the distance remaining to cross the valley. at this point the light made a sudden change of direction and headed south at such extreme speed as to travel aprox. 50 miles in 1-2 seconds. as we stood trying to evaluate what we saw; an air police patrol drove by and said "what are you doing?" when we asked if they had seen the object, they told us in very commanding tone that we had seen nothing.
content.summary: Moved from west to east at speed of small airplain,  made 90 degree turn and traveled about 50 miles in 1-2 seconds, vanished

content.detailedDescription: We were driving north on idaho st. at 12:35 pm. i looked up, where the flight path normally is for the planes flying into lax. however, i saw a pink line in the skin, but upon taking a picture, it was boomerang shape. i continued to watch it at the red light and took three pictures. two of the pictures have airplanes inside them. when the light turned green, i continued north on idaho st. and pulled into the gas station on the corner of la habra blvd. i then took another picture that clearly was the boomerang shape. we then drove east on la habra blvd to head home. while driving north on euclid ave above la habra blvd. the object disappeared.

content.detailedDescription: I was sitting on the couch watching judge judy.  i had the urge to go outside and take pictures of the sun. i took six pictures of the sun, while taking to the pictures i didn't see anything, the sun was to bright but when i got badck inside and looked at the photos that's when i noticed glowing round blue object. i thought it was  a trick of the sun or shadow but this object was in all the photos not only that but in each photo the object was in a different spot rising and moving west. i think i was a ufo or every cell in my boby is telling me it is nibiru in one photo there is a purple glow or haze around it reminding of the winged disk from sumeria or ancient egypt. i have the photos in my phone might know how to send them from this lap-top.

content.detailedDescription:
!968-69 guantanamo bay cuba, i was a marine on fence line duty. all of us marine's were amazed at the amount of ufo activity over and around this base. virtually every night ufo's were flying over head with altitudes of less than 300 ft. most of these ufo's were approximately 50 to 100 ft across but to the naked eye came off as a dull hazy hull with a small red light trailing behind it. when i stood guard duty on the south side of the base i witnessed on many, many nights ufo's landing and taking off out of the ocean. there were large blue lights moving around after their landing in the ocean and then slowly dimming down as they obviously descended deeper.
now, the most exciting event came when i stood guard duty at the main gate. it was approximately 7pm (dark) when i stepped out of the guard shack and looked across the fence at the deserted cuban guard house when something caught eye. behind the cuban guard shack near the ground was a huge white cloud with a blue/white = baby blue pulsating light in the middle of it. i asked my partner to verify what i was seeing because now it had risen up and over the cuban shack heading for us. just then, the observation tower call us and was yelling to get the hell out of there. by this time it was to late because the ufo was now above me and my partner.
there was no noise at all, just this big beautiful white cloud with a blue/white pulsating light. we stood there for several minutes just looking at it, then the sgt. of the guard ordered us to leave the guard shack. we walked to the barracks which is on a hill about 200 ft away where we could observe from a safe distance.
base intelligence arrive with a crew of people who began filming this ufo which lasted about 3 hours before moving west down the fence line. the ufo traveled about 1/4 of a mile, stopped for a moment, then like a bullet, shot straight up in the air until it disappeared. i would love to go back there just to see if the ufo's are still showing up. the dates that i have put down is a shot in the dark because that was 50 years ago.
content.summary: Large white cloud w/blue-white pulsating light others with dull hull with small red like darting around behind it.

content.detailedDescription: it was a summer evening my stepmother was watching the river as she always did at night time she started screaming for us kids to come out and look  at what she was watching  in the sky as myself and two stepbrothers ran into the front  porch  we witnessed a huge oval shaped object hovering above the water approximately 300 feet above the water the object was approximately 3 to 500 feet long and had bright white lights  surrounding the object. there were white lights approximately 10 to 50 feet wide they came out from the center of the craft straight down to the water and hover over the water for  approximately 5 to 15 seconds before shooting  off at a 25 to 35Â° angle in a south west direction when these crafts left the water,  they were gone in a blink of an eye and left a light trail  behind them. we watched the object come out of the center of the big craft one by one for approximately  10 to 15 minutes.  there were approximately 25 to 35 objects they came out from the center of the big craft once the last object left the craft the big craft  then hovered over the water for approximately five more minutes then drifted slowly and a southeast  direction flying almost directly above our house when the object was passed our house it made no sound there were no noise no vibration nothing all the lights turned off and the craft shot upwards at an extremely high rate of speed and the craft  disappeared  into the night sky.  for the next month or two we all sat out on the porch looking for these lights again we did not ever see any other lights in the same area. it appeared to us the crafts that came out  of the center of a large object and drop down to the water it was almost like they were getting water for fuel or something. there was no sound whatsoever  and to this day it has messed with my head tremendously i don't tell people what i saw for fear of being ridiculed. i know what my stepmother my two brothers and myself witness there was a tv show called operation bluebook that we tried to contact to let them know about the ufos that we witnessed. we called  the local authorities to report the incident as well and no one ever contacted us back. over the next few weeks i asked other people in the neighborhood if they had  witnessed anything  and one older gentleman said he saw exactly what we saw. i have tried doing some research to see if anyone else on either side of the chesapeake bay have witnessed the same exact thing that we saw  and i have not been able to find anything. the area that we saw all these objects is at the top of the chesapeake bay where the bay meets the rivers  by turkey point. aberdeen proving ground is directly across from our old house but there was nothing ever like this before or after.
content.summary: Large oval shaped object with little objects dropping from it

content.detailedDescription: It happened today at 1:56 pm. i was at 1-75 north bound. the sky was clear, no clouds at all. i saw something white moving west to east super, extra fast. i have no cars in front of me then i slow down my car so i can see the object better. i know that  closed there is a fll airport and i thought it was a learjet. it was like a cigar shape or maybe a bullet style.  then i slow  down more and saw it changes from white to gray and then disappeared in front of my eyes. i tried to find it but it was gone. i did not take a picture, everything was so fast and i was driving.
content.summary: White fast object that change color from white to silver and then disappeared.

content.detailedDescription: I was in the air force,at langley afb, hampton, va. i was in the 48th fis squadron. we maintained two aircraft, armed and ready to "scramble" on a moment's notice. late one night in march or april of 1972, at about 8:00 pm, a blimp appeared on radar that caused our aircraft to be scrambled because it was inside us air territory, the planes were out about an hr, when one of the pilots began screaming over the radio that they were confronting a "ufo", it was an orb and seemingly clear. the ranking officer ordered to fire missiles at it.The squadron was put on immediate lock down! guarded by armed m.P.S, the cameraman who develops was immediately called to come to his shop, a.S.A.P., when the two aircraft returned to base, the pilots came inside. one was clearly in shock, and just kept repeating, over and over, " a f#####g flying saucer!We fired at it, but they just went right through it". several unmarked station wagons appeared in the parking lot and men in af long coats, entered the building and immediately began debriefing both pilots in the command post upstairs. a man in glasses came into my shop and asked me if i had spoken to either pilot or had they spoke to me. my response was, "no." the next morning both pilots had been transferred during the night. one went to the pentagon the other was assigned out west, i think edwards afb, in california. i never saw either pilot again, film from the nosecones of their aircraft was confiscated. my immediate ncoic, told me to keep my mouth shut if i didn't want to be reassigned. so i kept quiet.
content.summary: 2-f106,air force fighters were scrambled from langley afb to intercept a ufo on radar. one pilot returned in shock, saying over and over, "damn ufo!". both pilots were transfered overnight out west and one to pentigon.

content.detailedDescription: My brother came in for a family vacation and he was staying up at our cabin in new lisbon wisconsin.  for several evenings we would go out on the deck and catch up on times and watching satellites for several evenings go by without incident. one of the evenings as we were talking and watching satellites passing over for several hours watching them and looking at the stars, there were a few scattered clouds but a very clear night to be star gazing and watching satellites .  as we were looking toward the stars we thought we had noticed another satellite and were following it across the sky almost at a 10 o'clock position when it went behind a cloud.  we never took our eyes off the object and waited and waited and waited.  as we watched the cloud go by which was moving slower then the object was the object never appeared again!  we both looked at each other and said did you see that, where did it go.  fort mccoy is close to us in monroe wisconsin.  we are in our 60s and thought people would think we were making this up but this did happen.  till this day we have told our loved ones but no one else as fear of being labeled nuts or making this up.
content.summary: Round and bright light size of a satellite

content.detailedDescription:
Hi.In 1978 me and 4 friends were partying , drinking beer and smoking pot in the superstition mountains. 
around midnight,mark tobin 
, our driver,decided to crash out in his car while we keep partying. 
about an hour later,paul lelevier and kevin hargis decided to go hiking into the mountains to a place called hackleberry.This is a place we had all hiked to before. 
me and eric starr smith stayed at our campsite around the campfire while paul and kevin went hiking.
this is where our sighting began
approximately 2 to 2:30 i noticed a white light way off in the distance. after about  15 minutes i remember noticing that the light seemed closer to our location and mentioned to eric that it looked like it was getting closer to our location. he agreed with me.
it was moving very slowly and definitely coming in our direction and took at least 45 minutes to get to us. when it was about 200ft away and maybe 4 or 500ft in elevation away from us it hovered there for about 5 minutes. 
it was saucer shaped with white stationary lights at spaced intervals around the craft. it was around 100ft across . it was smooth on the sides and the domed top but on the underside was irregular and looked like the irregularities were covering up whatever was underneath .
needless to say , we were very freaked out and scared.I remember asking eric if he could hear anything from the object as there was no sound at all from the craft,he could not.I remember hearing the snap,crackle,pop of the fire trying to hear  some type of noise. i also remember thinking 'i wonder if they are going to take me '.
as slowly as it approached us it left at a 45 degree angle away from us.
when paul and kevin  returned from  hiking we told them what had happened and they just laughed at us . mark,fast asleep, saw nothing. 
i was only 16 when this happened.
as a side note, eric starr smith whom i witnessed the event with, was arrested for murdering his own son years later on a new mexico highway and given life in prison  for his crime.
content.summary: Watched a light in the sky slowly approach and hover then slowly move away

content.detailedDescription:

so i got out of my machine and video recorded what i could. this was the first one.
after calling everyone i knew another one appeared from the same direction.
i was ready... video captured this one quick. 
now these were red orbs, on the recording you can't tell. it was at night and on a smart phone.
i followed them both until they literally went into space..

content.detailedDescription:
My father called me over while he was burning trash in a rural area. i was 7 years old and it was dark out. my father pointed out a very large orb hovering over our neighbors house about a quarter mile away. it looked like the moon or a huge glowing balloon but it was the size of a house just hovering there. my father said it was a flying saucer. it scared me so i ran into the house. when my father came in he said it just disappeared. 
a few days later my neighbor died.
content.summary: Globe hovering over house.

content.detailedDescription:
I am now 57 years old. i have recently retired from a 32 year teaching career. when i was 10 years old my older brother was making a short wave radio as a science project for his seventh grade science fair. as he was fine-tuning the radio we were passing around the headphones attached to the radio. the only person who heard anything was me. i heard a unrecognizable voice speaking a language which to me, at least at the time, was not of this world. that night as i was lying in bed, the voice resumed. but this time there was no headphones, radio, and everyone else in the house was asleep. the voice came back to me during ensuing nights beginning to affect my sleep and even life. i remember one night i awakened my brother who this time became angry since it wasn't the first time. 
occurrences that were apparently associated with those aforementioned  were happening at about this same time. bright lights were running along the walls of my bedroom at night. not constantly, but from time to time. 
here's the most significant part of all of this and why i'm choosing to report these occurrences...One night my mother came to my room to check on me. she saw a bright light, about the size of a golfball on the center of my lower back coming through my covers. she put her hand over the light to check to make sure where from where it was being generated.   she was startled to see that it was coming from me and not from above. she didn't tell me about this until many years later when i was teaching and these things were obviously in my past. 
above i left vague details about specific times, etc. because these occurrences were long ago, happening over several months. i was 10 years old. i had no more occurrences of this sort happen to me at any age before or after.
content.summary: Combination of a light coming from me and a not-from-this-world voice occurring over a few months.

content.detailedDescription:
i was a teenager camping out in the backyard with two other friends. we were all laying on our backs while star gazing around 3am. we watched the sky for over an hour when i spotted two stars running parallel across the sky heading sw. after pointing them out to my friends i became frightened thinking the stars were falling as in biblical prophesy and exclaimed "its the end of the world!". as we continued to watch the two stars they quickly split in opposite 90 degree directions and continued across the sky until out of sight.
     they appeared to be very high in the sky as i said, i thought they were stars. they also appeared to be moving really fast.
     after we lost sight of them we were excited knowing they must have been ufo's because nothing on earth could move that way.
     we continued to watch the skies till dawn hoping to spot some more but no luck. no one believed us of course.
content.summary: Two lights resembling stars ran paralle high in the sky then both took a 90 degree angle in opposite directions till out of sight.

content.detailedDescription: I was training a client outside of my house and we went for a run. after we came back and as we were walking in the house, i noticed one very distinct spherical orb just hovering in the sky about a few hundred meters nw from the sun. i thought it was odd how it just seemed to sit still in the sky for so long (about 2 min) and pointed it out to my roommate who came outside and witnessed it also. we notice it starts to very slowly move more east towards the sun almost as if it were in a floating or hovering motion. looked very reflective luke an airplane but distinctly orb shaped. sometimes would glow but could be the reflection.I know it wasn't a plane because there were a few in the area s of where we are as there is a small airport close by and it looked/moved nothing like any plane i've seen in the sky. my bf came outside to see and out of nowhere it seems two more appears and are almost in the shape of orions belt constellation. we witness these orbs hovering slowly and 4 more appear out of nowhere. there are now about 7 orbs in a triangular like formation, occasionally appearing and disappearing but in tue same spots. we witness this for a good 5 minutes and then i sadly had to leave due to my client being on a time constraint. i try to capture it on my phone but for some reason i was not able to see them on camera. not sure if it was their doing or that it was too far, considering my phone camera is actually not bad. blew my mind but i did not need any more convincing as i have noticed weird stuff like this in the area, but mostly at night. and i had two other witnesses this time.
content.summary: Fleet of star-like orbs (glowing or reflective?) above commerce, tx

content.detailedDescription: My in laws had gone to the er,earlier in the evening. i came outside to smoke a cigarette and looked up towards the eastern sky and i saw a bright light about the size of a golfball. larger than the star nearest to it. i watched for a few moments and without taking my eyes off of this light, i grabbed my cell phone out of my pocket and voice messaged my husband to come outside now. as i continued to watch it appeared to reach out towards us and retreat. it did this several times over the course of 45 minutes. during our experience my husband grabbed his spotting scope to get a better visual and he claimed there were more than one lights and that some seemed to be circling a center or main structure. we both saw this unexplained phenomenon until the light simply retracted out of sight.
content.summary: I noticed a bright light in the east northeast sky. it was close to 3 am. i watch for a few seconds & called for my husband to come out. we watched this light for approximately 45 minutes.

content.detailedDescription: I arrived at the youth camp, outside rapid city sd around 11:30 pm. i had been working there as a night supervisor, making sure the youths didn't leave the camp.  just as i pulled into camp the ufo glided over the treetops and the building.  it stayed there for some time, bringing other workers out of the building, to see what it was, then glided away.  there was no sound, just the blinking light on the bottom.  later, threw the time i worked there, i noticed children would stagger back into to the buildings, acting like the were drunk.  looking back, i wish i would have checked into the matter better. note: years after, i always had a feeling of being under observation. i am sorry about the insufficient data, but this took place in 1973, there wasn't much for multimedia forms back then,  this facility was run by the government. i am reporting this now because i wanted someone to know, without thinking i was making it up. i don't remember the people i worked with.  quit shortly after the sighting.
content.summary: Round disk, 7-8 lights on bottom, no noise,slowly glided over trees
